title: Wholesale Price of Print Cloth, Mills for United States
notes:
Series Has Been Subdivided Into Four Variables: (1)-- Original Data, 1890-1913; (2)--Original Data, 1914-1943; (3)-- Original Data, 1943-1946; (4)-- Original Data, 1946-1958. Data Refers To Print Cloth, 39", 80X80, 4.00 Yards Per Pound. Source: Bls, "Prices And Price Relatives For Individual Commodities In The Revised Index: 1947-1950, Group 3, Textile Products And Apparel", February 1952; Bls Bulletin No. 1143; Monthly Issues Of "Wholesale Prices"

This NBER data series m04086d appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
